'''"'Til Death Do Us Part"''' is a short adventure for [[Dungeons & Dragons]] 2{{nd}} edition published in [[Dungeon magazine 29|''Dungeon'' #29]].
{{TOC limit|2}}
{{Quote|"'Til Death Do Us Part" is an AD&D® adventure to be played by a group of 5&ndash;6 player characters of levels 8-10 (about 50 levels total). Set in the [[Forgotten Realms|FORGOTTEN REALMS™]] fantasy world, it is designed as an extended random encounter for those [[adventurer]]s in search of the ruins of [[Myth Drannor]], to add an air of mystery and menace to that quest. A well balanced party, including a [[paladin]] and [[cleric]] capable of [[turn undead|turning]] powerful [[undead]], is most likely to survive the hit-and-run tactics employed in this adventure.<ref>{{Cite dungeon/29/'Til Death Do Us Part|50}}}}

